citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 1:20 pm on
15-JAN-20.
The inspectors waited at the facility and called the available phone number on file and left a message. Additionally
the inspectors left a note for the licensee to contact them regarding this attempted inspection.
Additional Inspectors
Radzai Christina, Veterinary Medical Officer
